acceptOwnership().details: The new owner accepts the ownership transfer.

params._owner: The owner address for this contract (and BondMarket).
params._staking: The address of the staking contract (used by BondMarket).
params._uranoToken: The address of the URANO token contract.
params._usdc: The address of the USDC token contract.

createuShare(string,string,uint256,(uint.details: Only the contract owner can call this function.

params._name: The name of the uShare token (e.g., "XYZ uShare Token").
params._symbol: The symbol of the uShare token (e.g., "XYZUSH").
params._totalSupply: The total supply of the uShare token to be minted.
params._uShareInfoParams: A struct containing uShare sale parameters.

owner().details: Returns the address of the current owner.

pendingOwner().details: Returns the address of the pending owner.

renounceOwnership().details: Leaves the contract without owner. It will not be possible to call `onlyOwner` functions. Can only be called by the current owner. NOTE: Renouncing ownership will leave the contract without an owner, thereby disabling any functionality that is only available to the owner.

setuShareId(address,bytes32).details: Can only be called by the uShareMarket contract.      Reverts if the uShareId is already set for this token.

params._uShareId: The unique identifier to set for this uShare.
params._uShareToken: The address of the uShare token.

transferOwnership(address).details: Starts the ownership transfer of the contract to a new account. Replaces the pending transfer if there is one. Can only be called by the current owner. Setting `newOwner` to the zero address is allowed; this can be used to cancel an initiated ownership transfer.

constructor.notice: Deploys a new BondMarket contract and sets up the factory.

createuShare(string,string,uint256,(uint.notice: Creates a new uShare token and initializes a uShare sale in the uShareMarket.

i_uShareMarket().notice: The uShareMarket contract instance created and used by this factory.

s_uShareId(address).notice: Maps a uShare token address to its uShareId.

setuShareId(address,bytes32).notice: Sets the uShareId for a given uShare token address.
